#: BaseBillet/templates/reunion/views/account/balance.html:152
msgid ""
"The TiBillet, recharged online, are the only currency we can refund online. "
"For local currencies (recharged in cash or at a bank terminal on site), "
"please contact the collective that issued them."
msgstr ""
"Les TiBillets, rechargés en ligne, sont la seule monnaie que nous pouvons "
"aussi rembourser en ligne. Pour les monnaies locales (rechargées en espèces "
